{"tid":1929453,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國出疫苗 - 冇事喇 - 美開始試驗新冠疫苗 西雅圖第一批病患接受注射","createTime":"2020-03-17T02:59:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-17T08:17:29.000Z","uid":49784,"like":324,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":93,"replies":[{"pid":"b462d535a1336cee2b5ae0303965b929846f6c26","tid":1929453,"uid":49784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T02:59:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20200317000930-260408\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinatimes.com%2Frealtimenews%2F20200317000930-260408&d=AC0Zr9jWFF2OJ189utQw8LZiocJRpRWN%2FMrNqpcM%2BY8%3D&h=92ca4ce3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20200317000930-260408</a><br />\n<br />\n美國醫療研究團隊開始進行新冠肺炎疫苗的臨床試驗，16日在美國重災區華盛頓州展開第一批病患注射，疫苗研發進度領先全球。<br />\n<br />\n根據美聯社報導，華盛頓研究中心(Kaiser Permanente Washington Research Institute)於16日開始試驗新冠肺炎的疫苗，第一批自願接受臨床試驗的病患共有45位，當日接受第一劑，一個月後再注射第二劑。"},{"pid":"300ac553791649b20e02150144a4e2d8a89e0e22","tid":1929453,"uid":49784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T03:00:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"257e0122ce205c847ff75eface8ac8b4b8f4ec21","tid":1929453,"uid":121146,"like":213,"dislike":3,"score":210,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T03:01:47.000Z","msg":"美國佬先有權表示  信政府  唔驚 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb56bb1ffcc1b8563117332d21023393e5f5baa0","tid":1929453,"uid":49784,"like":15,"dislike":2,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T03:01:54.000Z","msg":"世界又回復正常"},{"pid":"a3ab5e00b0c8f920b241e0adc8e81b5b302603fb","tid":1929453,"uid":30791,"like":30,"dislike":2,"score":28,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T03:02:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 幫患者打疫苗?"},{"pid":"96208e1fd534bcd462e97045c6f420328bae2b90","tid":1929453,"uid":49784,"like":6,"dislike":5,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a3ab5e00b0c8f920b241e0adc8e81b5b30260